    {
      "id": "9adffdf1_63c66f4b",
      "file_path": "sources/hv-collector-utils/src/main/kotlin/org/onap/dcae/collectors/veshv/utils/logging/reactive_logging.kt",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "Maybe we could create ContextualLogger(Logger, ClientContext) implementation that would hold ClientContext and delegate to logger methods with ClientContext.MDC usage?\n\nFor example let's take VesHvCollector class - every call to logger in this class is passing along also clientContext object. So we could simply hold reference to ContextualLogger(HvVes.logger, clientContext) object which we would pass to all calls inside reactive_logging. \n\nI believe this could reduce the \"pollution\" of interfaces inside the component",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3701,
        "name": "Filip Krzywka",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "filip.krzywka@nokia.com",
        "username": "fkrzywka"
      },
      "updated": "2018-12-10 11:42:58.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
